Sentencas: The feasibility of a direct internal reforming (DIR) solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) running on wet palm-biodiesel fuel (BDF) was demonstrated.
Titulo: Feasibility of palm-biodiesel fuel for a direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Simultaneous production of H2-rich syngas and electricity from BDF could be achieved.
Titulo: Feasibility of palm-biodiesel fuel for a direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A power density of 0.32Wcm2 was obtained at 0.4 A cm2 and 800 degrees C under steam to carbon ratio of 3.5.
Titulo: Feasibility of palm-biodiesel fuel for a direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Subsequent durability testing revealed that a DIR-SOFC running on wet palm-BDF exhibited a stable voltage of around 0.8V at 0.2 A cm2 for more than 1month with a degradation rate of approximately 15 % / 1000h.
Titulo: Feasibility of palm-biodiesel fuel for a direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The main cause of the degradation was an increase in the ohmic resistance.
Titulo: Feasibility of palm-biodiesel fuel for a direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell
